name: Nude in a Fascinator Hat
description: Feminine nude in a burst of spring colors. Flowing lines and textural movements collide in an explosion of warm peachy tones. Nude in a Fascinator Hat is a celebration of minimalism, flowy movements and the harmonies of human relationships with nature. A limited edition series of 20,  each artwork is as simple in rendition and complex in its emotions. Digital Illustration.  5400px X 7200px 300dpi
